---
---
<section class="product-section">
  <div class="wrap product">
    <div class="product__media">
      <div class="phone-frame">
        <div class="phone-frame__screen">
          <img src="/app-mobile-screenshot.png" alt="Pantalla principal de INOUT mostrando el balance total" />
        </div>

        <div class="callout callout--in">
          <span class="pip"><i data-lucide="trending-up"></i></span>
          <span>+S/&nbsp;1,000.00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="callout callout--out">
          <span class="pip"><i data-lucide="trending-down"></i></span>
          <span>&minus;S/&nbsp;372.90</span>
        </div>
        <div class="callout callout--cat">
          <span class="pip"><i data-lucide="layers"></i></span>
          <span>4 categorias activas</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow-row"><span class="tick"></span> Tu pantalla principal</div>
      <h2 class="section__h2 product__title">Claridad que se siente dise&ntilde;ada.</h2>
      <p class="section__lead">
        Una tarjeta navy. Un numero grande. Tres lineas honestas. Asi luce tu situacion financiera en INOUT &mdash; sin graficos confusos ni gamification innecesaria.
      </p>

      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon green"><i data-lucide="zap"></i></div>
          <div>
            <h3>Registra en menos de 30 segundos</h3>
            <p>Dos botones grandes: IN para ingresos, OUT para gastos. Monto, categoria, listo. Sin asistentes ni pasos opcionales.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon navy"><i data-lucide="trending-up"></i></div>
          <div>
            <h3>Tu balance, siempre arriba</h3>
            <p>La tarjeta navy del inicio te muestra balance total, ingresos, gastos y neto del mes. Todo de un vistazo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon"><i data-lucide="shapes"></i></div>
          <div>
            <h3>Categorias que s&iacute; usas</h3>
            <p>Alimentacion, transporte, casa, educacion, gimnasio. 24 categorias hechas para la vida diaria, no para contadores.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .product-section { padding-top: 0; }
  .product {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 96px);
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .product { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .product__media { position: relative; }
  .product__title { font-size: clamp(36px, 4.6vw, 60px); }

  .phone-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 380px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    aspect-ratio: 9 / 19.5;
    background: var(--color-ink);
    border-radius: 52px;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
  }
  .phone-frame::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 14px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 110px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--color-ink);
    border-radius: 999px;
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .phone-frame__screen {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 42px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-sage);
  }
  .phone-frame__screen img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top center;
  }

  .callout {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--color-white-pure);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    padding: 8px 14px 8px 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .callout .pip {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: var(--color-white-pure);
  }
  .callout :global(.lucide) { width: 14px; height: 14px; }

  .callout--in  { left: -28px; top: 18%; }
  .callout--in  .pip { background: var(--color-primary-green); color: var(--color-ink); }
  .callout--out { right: -28px; top: 36%; }
  .callout--out .pip { background: var(--color-action-red); }
  .callout--cat { left: -16px; bottom: 22%; }
  .callout--cat .pip { background: var(--color-navy-deep); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .callout--in  { left: 0; }
    .callout--out { right: 0; }
    .callout--cat { left: 8px; }
  }

  .feature-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 28px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }
  .feature {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: start;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
  }
  .feature:first-child {
    border-top: 0;
    padding-top: 0;
  }
  .feature__icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-white-pure);
  }
  .feature__icon.green { background: var(--color-primary-green); color: var(--color-ink); }
  .feature__icon.navy  { background: var(--color-navy-deep); color: var(--color-white-pure); }
  .feature__icon :global(.lucide) { width: 22px; height: 22px; stroke-width: 2; }
  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .feature p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-ink-60);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
